          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to furnish free comprehensive mental health care to any former member of the Armed Forces, including reservists. Additionally, the bill makes any former member of the Armed Forces, including reservists, eligible for readjustment counseling and related mental health services.</p> <ul> </ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-11-08T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
